Module JavaDataStructures
Package JavaDS.Sorters

Interface ISorter<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of data elements being sorted.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BubbleSort, HeapSort, InsertionSort, MergeSort, QuickSort, SelectionSort, SuperSort
    public interface ISorter<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    Interface for sorting algorithms. Implementing classes can sort collections of Comparable extending data elements.
    Author:
    Tom Esser
